[assistant] Fixed the failing authentication routine test.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Cause:
[assistant] - HSQLDB `2.4.1` does not resolve a Java external authentication function returning `String[]` as SQL `VARCHAR ARRAY`.
[assistant] - It expects a return type resolvable as SQL array, such as `java.sql.Array`.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Change:
[assistant] - Updated `RoutineMethods.authenticate(...)` to return a simple test `java.sql.Array` implementation backed by `String[]`.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Commit amended:
[assistant] - `8584802674 Add HSQLDB Routine dynamic access tests`
[assistant] 
[assistant] I did not run tests, per the original instruction.
